{"tid":672253,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有社交障礙","createTime":"2018-05-20T23:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T01:10:53.000Z","uid":81190,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f6445adec0ff9e0388b4bbfa5b6096c36df975","tid":672253,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T23:09:45.000Z","msg":"而家搞到咁我真係唔知點算好<br />\n番工人地叫我做嘢我又唔係好聽得慢，人地指個方向我又唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通咁就一世"},{"pid":"235fb51df3bad14d80e2d95ae4e6eae7bab01323","tid":672253,"uid":81190,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T23:42:57.000Z","msg":"講嘢得罪人又唔知，又唔識睇人眉頭眼額，做嘢「論盡」，真係唔知可以點算好。屋企人指嚿嘢我又唔知佢指乜。我可以點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好辛苦呀<br />\n我想做個正常人咋，點解可以咁難"},{"pid":"8cc2635ab94e97e6edacf3a09b69187ae04f68e8","tid":672253,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T23:51:57.000Z","msg":"學, 留意其他人做緊乜, 諗緊乜, tune到自己接近其他人思想言行舉止. 有錢就睇醫生."},{"pid":"fe6d48784dcdf9ed40e41dbc63939f196b8236cc","tid":672253,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T23:52:59.000Z","msg":"試下多d猜度他人"},{"pid":"039341362c3ca57d8020914dbe14a5f2538b2e33","tid":672253,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T23:53:33.000Z","msg":"唔明唔好扮明<br />\n問清問楚<br />\n做錯野仲衰<br />\n<br />\n做好「溝通」"},{"pid":"667b3fb8f91e658bb587de9452d05ab2f5dc7915","tid":672253,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8cc2635ab94e97e6edacf3a09b69187ae04f68e8","tid":672253,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T23:51:57.000Z","msg":"學, 留意其他人做緊乜, 諗緊乜, tune到自己接近其他人思想言行舉止. 有錢就睇醫生."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:02:24.000Z","msg":"我都有學呀，我都有跟呀<br />\n由中一發現自己同人有少少唔同我就所有嘢都學緊<br />\n但都仲係同人有唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我到而家都唔係好識聽反話、說話嘅潛台辭，人地指個位叫我執我都知執邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/